Translate ggplot2 object into a ggspec

gg2spec.Rd

Translate ggplot2 object into a ggspec

gg2spec(plt)

Arguments

plt

A ggplot2 object.

Value

list, a ggspec list.

Examples

library(ggplot2)
p <- ggplot(data = iris)
p <- p + geom_point(aes(x = Petal.Width, y = Petal.Length))
gg2spec(p)
